title: Match of the Day 2 - 7th December 2014 - HDTV X264
description:
SPORT: Match of the Day 2
On: BBC 1 HD     
Date: Sunday 7th December 2014 
Time: 22:30 to 23:35 

Mark Chapman presents highlights of Sunday's two Premier League matches, along with a look back at all of Saturday's action. West Ham hope to continue their winning record against Swansea, having taken the three points in their two previous Premier League meetings at Upton Park. In 2013 the Hammers went into this fixture in the relegation zone, but two goals from Kevin Nolan gave them a crucial victory. Plus Midlands rivals Aston Villa and Leicester meet in the league for the first time in over ten years, and both teams are desperate to take the bragging rights
